{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第十一回\"喜从天降\"讲述了楚留香、胡铁花、姬冰雁三人在龟兹国帐篷中讨论同行者中谁的武功最高。楚留香指出琵琶公主才是深藏不露的高手，正说间，吴青天前来传话，称龟兹王受琵琶公主之托向三人求亲，公主看中的正是胡铁花。胡铁花表面推辞，内心窃喜，在楚留香和姬冰雁的激将法下最终答应。深夜楚留香外出，发现王冲暗中注视石驼，琵琶公主主动找楚留香攀谈，流露出对他的好感。随后吴青天带三人赴龟兹王帐中饮宴，龟兹王赠胡铁花猫儿眼宝石为见面礼，龟兹王妃抱病出见，亦赐下丰厚宝物。本章揭示了琵琶公主对楚留香与胡铁花的复杂情感，以及龟兹王对极乐之星下落的执念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这其中只有那王冲，较为可疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了!我看'王冲'这两个字，绝不会是他的真名实姓。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人不但行踪有些诡秘，而且武功也深藏不露，他如此掩饰自己的行藏，必定有所图谋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看这些人中，武功最高的就是此人么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道不是?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看并不是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "琵琶公主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错!她若不会武功，就绝不会有那么高的眼力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且她比那王冲更深藏不露，外表看来，竟好像是弱不禁风的样子，内功若非已有了很深的火候，又怎能将劲气收敛得丝毫不露?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "倾国倾城的塞外公主，竟是个深藏不露的武林高手，这倒的确有趣得很，有趣的很!",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帐外之人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三位还没有睡么?在下特来拜候。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下的来意，三位只怕是再也不会想得到的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不瞒你说，我们现在正在猜哩!",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实在下也是受人所托而来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "受人所托?谁托了你?托你来做什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下是受龟兹王之托，来向三位求亲的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求亲?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位王爷倒真的妙不可言，他难道想将我们三人都招为驸马不成?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求亲的对象，自然只不过是三位中的一位，而且这也不是王爷的意思，而是大公主自己一见之下，芳心便已暗许。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知这位公主究竟……咳咳……究竟是看上了谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公主亲眼瞧上的，正是阁下。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙极!妙极!这位公主倒真有赏识英雄的慧眼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "荒唐!荒唐!她怎么会看上我的?你弄错了吧?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此大事，在下怎会弄错!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你一定是错了，再回去问问吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "用不着再问，只要阁下答应，在下便可回去复命了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此大事，怎能在仓卒之间决定，阁下也该容他考虑考虑才是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，在下等半个时辰再来……三位有所不知，这倒不是在下着急，而是那位公主……哈哈……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恭喜!恭喜!你打了这么多年的光棍，想不到竟是等着来做驸马的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死公鸡，你听听，难得有一次女人看上我而没看上他，他就要拈酸吃醋。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我吃醋?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你并不是吃醋，你只不过心里有些不舒服而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个连酒铺里小老板娘都瞧不上的人，忽然会被个公主瞧上了，这岂非好像天上忽然掉下个大馅饼么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看他得意成什么样子，咱们不如现在就把吴青天找进来吧，免得他们两人都等得着急。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么不行?你难道不答应?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然不答应。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看你如此开心，又早已对那位公主倾倒得五体投地，人家替你倒酒时，你几乎连骨头都酥了，现在你又为何不答应?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老实说，我对那位公主的确有点喜欢，她瞧上的若不是我，我或许会比老臭虫更伤心失望，但她若真要嫁我，那却万万不可以。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不可以?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不可以就是不可以。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看他只怕是老毛病又犯了，别人不喜欢他，他却像苍蝇见了血似的盯住人家，别人喜欢他，他反而要摆架子了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孙子才有这意思，我只不过……只不过……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过怎样?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们想想，像我这样的人，怎么能娶个公主做老婆?我养得活她么?若要我乖乖地跟着她做驸马，那更是死也办不到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想得未免太远了，而咱们的问题却是现在。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，人家如此盛意，你若不答应，我们的计划便要落空，我看你无论如何，这次都非答应不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们若逼我，我可要逃了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有我和楚留香在这里，你逃得了么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是我的终身大事，你们为何要逼我?你们还算是我的老朋友么!你们……你们简直卖友求荣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，我就去替你回绝他吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这本是我们三个人的事，他既不肯替朋友设想，我们又有什么法子，明天被人家一齐赶走也就算了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只是有些替他可惜……倾国倾城的美丽公主，又是深藏不露的武林高手，这样的妻子他不要，不后悔一辈子才怪。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可怜那多情的公主，她听了这话，又不知该多伤心?",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慢走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为何慢走，让她早些死了心不好么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我考虑很久，已决定为朋友牺牲了，谁让咱们有这么多年的交情呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行!不行!婚事乃终身大事，我们做朋友的怎能让你牺牲自己，我还是去回绝了他们吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除此之外，还有……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还有什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想，娶个公主虽麻烦，但总比在沙漠里兜圈子麻烦少得多，何况，我……我也实在不忍令人家伤心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就知道你这毛病了，敬酒是不吃的，偏偏总要去吃罚酒。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "帐外之人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么敬酒罚酒?在下只是在等着吃喜酒哩!",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黄莺般语声",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不是早就想睡觉了么?怎地却又变成了夜游神?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里的夜游神，只怕也不只在下一个吧?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "别人我不管，你半夜三更不睡觉，是不是又想偷看人家洗澡?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来也许真有这意思，但现在夜游神实在太多了，我还是去睡吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "喂……你回来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我问你，你为什么不理我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "在下怎会不理公主?只不过，既然没什么事，在下还是想去睡了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "谁说我没有事找你?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "公主有什么事找在下?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我只是想问你，为什么别人叫你老臭虫?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我问你的话，你为何不说?",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "这话你本不该问我的，是么?是谁叫了我这名字，你就该问谁去，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "text": "吴兄大功告成了么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下已回复过王爷，王爷实在开心得很，他虽然知道三位旅途劳顿，但却又实在开心得非和三位聊聊不可。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也无妨，如此大喜之日，反正我们也是睡不着的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不管你说什么，这句话我非得问出来不可，你逃也逃不了的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，王爷已在他帐篷里备好了宵夜的酒，就请三位过去吧，做媒的两条腿已快跑断了，这杯酒少不得也是要喝的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们来了，好!好!菜是热的，快坐下来喝一杯。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_qing_tian",
      "speaker_name": "吴青天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢坐下来，未来的女婿，总该先拜见岳父才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "是呀!快跪下磕头。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "好!好!",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "天方之石，佩之吉祥，你收下吧!",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "如此厚赐，怎敢拜领?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "老泰山所赐的见面之礼，若不拜领，便是不敬，你还是收下吧!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王妃的病体已有了起色，就让她出来坐坐也好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_bai_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吴白云",
      "listener": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "text": "莫非王妃也想出来瞧瞧女婿么?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此，她缠绵病榻已有许久，不想今日有了喜事，她竟能出来走动了，莫非这就是中土人士所谓的冲喜所致?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不快扶王妃坐下，快……外面的帘子为何还不拉起?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "就是他。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_zi_wang_fei",
      "speaker_name": "龟兹王妃",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "好!很好!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这是我母亲给你，收下吧!",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    }
  ],
